    "Id": "chassisdef_walker_WLK-B2",
    "Name": "Walker",
    "Details": "The WLK-B2 is a 20-ton security mech built around mobility and crowd control. Three jump jets spread across the center and side torsos provide 90 meters of jump capacity for urban and rural terrain navigation. Twin Machine Guns in the left arm default to rubber rounds for non-lethal work. A Medium and Small Laser in the right arm handle situations requiring lethal force. A head-mounted Searchlight supports night operations. Four tons of Heavy Industrial armor offers minimal protection against anything heavier.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Ubiquitous</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.7</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
