  "YangsThoughts": "Concordat Telecom built these for under a million C-Bills a unit which tells you everything about what they were going for. Taurian Concordat needed cheap security across dozens of border worlds and this is what they got. Spread all over unstable planets along the Periphery and Federated Suns border. Don't put it up against anything with real armor but for keeping local populations in line it did the job well enough.",
